author: prickett
msg: A time zone schema complete with diagrams of the overall data structure
of the xml schema. This was contributed by Mike George. Thanks Mike.
This will be the basis for our implemetation of time zones in periodicity.

author: prickett
msg: Removed dependency on core from the war task. This was causing the core task
to get called twice during the war task and wasting time.
Fixed war file to depend on our own copy of DefaultTop navigation.
Added the rest of the label constants to the TestTemplateLabels file
Added summary parameters to the evt_do_jrl.vm template.

author: prickett
msg: Added a VelocityScreen to populate the contents of the VelocityContext from
turbine.
Added a constants file that defines the labels for the test templates.

author: prickett
msg: Created a periodicity specific Top Navigation template that did not refer
to the default logo or UI object. This was causing errors when rendering the
screen.
The original file was pulled from the tdk and I guess it had more features than we really need at this point. This file will most likely be replaced with the
original file from the tdk when we have more time to figure out how to get it
to work.

author: prickett
msg: Capitalized the first letter of the template name because I ran into a bug
in TurbineVelocityService where the service did not recognize the templates
without a Capital letter and hence an exact match of the screen name.
I am not sure if this is something that has been fixed or if anyone else has
even seen this with the TurbineVelocityService.
